，6 日 4：00 核酸检测结果为 2 人阳性，分别为其母亲和妻子，两个孩子核酸检测为阴性。 目前，3 例阳性感染者已送定点医院隔离治疗。市委、市政府第一时间启动应急响应，组织开展流调溯源、隔离管控、核酸检测等工作，并对其活动场所进行环境采样检测及消杀，对相应区域已实行管控措施。后续情况将及时向社会公布。 宁波市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控 工作领导小组办公室 2021 年 12 月 6 日浙江宁波镇海区发现 3 例新冠核酸检测阳性"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-853fb71f3eb3a8574d7a7f1fc1ab8bc4_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "247 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/503972281"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IjsePn/mdkOcDEAMaCDc0Mjc0ODQzINKptY0GMAM4Z0AIcgk1MDM5NzIyODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1638767286.9431186", "card_id": "EV_12217676", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果郭艾伦是篮球老师，上他的课会是什么体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ab4e3d86731fb98547cc34c09bc0b0f6.jpg?"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "盐选推荐"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/xen/market/ecom-page/1441504820864094208"}}, "attached_info": "Cn0IjsePn/mdkOcDEBgaBDYzNDEgksmnjQZACXIIMTIyMTc2NzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZMoBPmh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS94ZW4vbWFya2V0L2Vjb20tcGFnZS8xNDQxNTA0ODIwODY0MDk0MjA48gEHCAESA3ZpcA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1638767286.943493", "card_id": "Q_45890852", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 442}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "潮汕牛肉火锅为什么火起来了，什么才是好的潮汕牛肉火锅？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近家附近开了好几家潮汕牛肉火锅，似乎一夜之间就火起来了⋯⋯这背后有啥原因吗？ 准备找机会去吃一下，请问什么样的潮汕牛肉火锅是比较正宗比较好吃的呢？ 吃的时候有什么讲究吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-371bb30600335d1f52d62dc231c88951_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "241 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/45890852"}}, "attached_in